steps.html_instructions: Head southeast on 6th Ave N toward Charlotte Ave
Slight right onto the US-31E N/Ellington Pkwy ramp
Take the exit onto I-65 N toward Louisville

Keep left at the fork to stay on I-65 N
Entering Kentucky
Take exit 93 for Blue Grass Pkwy toward Bardstown/Lexington

Take exit 72A to merge onto US-60 E/Lexington Rd toward Lexington
Continue to follow US-60 E
Merge onto KY-4 N/New Circle Rd via the ramp to I-75/I-64
Continue onto KY-4 N/US-421 BYP S/New Circle Rd
Turn left to merge onto I-64 E/I-75 S toward Knoxville/Ashland

Keep left at the fork to continue on I-64 E, follow signs for Winchester/Ashland
Entering West Virginia

Turn right onto US-60 E/Lee St W
Continue to follow US-60 E
